BTTTriggers.BTTPredefinedActionName: Run Apple Script (enter directly as text)
BTTTriggers.BTTInlineAppleScript: tell application "Finder"	activate	display dialog "Are you sure you want to shut down your computer?" buttons {"Cancel", "Restart", "Shut Down"} default button "Shut Down" with icon caution		if button returned of result is "Shut Down" then		shut down	else if button returned of result is "Restart" then		restart	end if	end tell
